item.title: Look of Disapproval + HAVE YOU TRIED TURNING IT OFF AND ON AGAIN?
item.description: When something goes wrong with a computer or any device turning it off and on again can seemingly fix the issue. A programmer or system administrator confronted with a bug or hardware issue may well ask HAVE YOU TRIED TURNING IT OFF AND ON AGAIN? / This...
